name: Dench.com
long_description:
Dench.com is an AI Intake Specialist Platform that take calls from prospective clients, talks to them, vets them, conflict checks, does follow-ups and books an appointment, or it forwards the call to a human after client pre-qualification.

We convert rejected cases into paid referrals through our referral network, to land law firms  huge profits over “wasted” leads.

For a simple demo, try calling (415) 997-2939 as someone with any legal dispute, property or other variety of issues you can possibly imagine.
one_liner: AI Secretary to pre-qualify leads for law firms
